name: ◙ Muchacha ◘
description:
Based on a portrait I found in a book while we where studying in class about the history of Caracas, the capital of my country. I found her expression of very mesmerizing and absorbent. I was captivated by her look. Her look expressed rudeness, she was somehow challenging the observer. I'll never forget the moment I saw her. 

This piece is mixed media, traditional + digital. 
I don't have information about the photographer, wich it's a shame.

//

Pencils & Digital collors. 
1102x1102 px
Oli Pino © 2020
